text: Kazyonno-Kuzhorsky () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Natyrbovskoye Rural Settlement of Koshekhablsky District, Adygea, Russia. The population of this khutor was 774 as of 2018. There are 9 streets. == References == Category:Rural localities in Koshekhablsky District
title: Kazyonno-Kuzhorsky
